<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ideedf6fe9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s1636i"><num value="1636i">§ 1636i.</num><heading> Termination of authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The authority provided by this subchapter terminates on <date date="2026-09-30">September 30, 2026</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ideedf6fea-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1946-08-14/ch966">Aug. 14, 1946, ch. 966</ref>, title II, § 260, as added <ref href="/us/pl/109/296/s1/a">Pub. L. 109–296, § 1(a)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-05">Oct. 5, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1464">120 Stat. 1464</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/111/239/s2/a/1">Pub. L. 111–239, § 2(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="2010-09-27">Sept. 27, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/2501">124 Stat. 2501</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/54/tI/s101/a">Pub. L. 114–54, title I, § 101(a)</ref>, <date date="2015-09-30">Sept. 30, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/513">129 Stat. 513</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/103/dO/tIII/s301/a">Pub. L. 117–103, div. O, title III, § 301(a)</ref>, <date date="2022-03-15">Mar. 15, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/788">136 Stat. 788</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/328/dA/tVII/s776/a">Pub. L. 117–328, div. A, title VII, § 776(a)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-29">Dec. 29, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/4509">136 Stat. 4509</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/118/42/dB/tVII/s793/a">Pub. L. 118–42, div. B, title VII, § 793(a)</ref>, <date date="2024-03-09">Mar. 9, 2024</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/138/120">138 Stat. 120</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/119/4/dA/tII/s1203/a">Pub. L. 119–4, div. A, title II, § 1203(a)</ref>, <date date="2025-03-15">Mar. 15, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/16">139 Stat. 16</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/119/37/dB/tVII/s774/a">Pub. L. 119–37, div. B, title VII, § 774(a)</ref>, <date date="2025-11-12">Nov. 12, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/557">139 Stat. 557</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="ideedf6feb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="ideedf6fec-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ideedf6fed-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2025—<ref href="/us/pl/119/37">Pub. L. 119–37</ref> substituted “2026” for “2025”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/119/4">Pub. L. 119–4</ref> substituted “2025” for “2024”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2024—<ref href="/us/pl/118/42">Pub. L. 118–42</ref> substituted “2024” for “2023”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2022—<ref href="/us/pl/117/328">Pub. L. 117–328</ref> substituted “2023” for “2022”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/117/103">Pub. L. 117–103</ref> substituted “2022” for “2020”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2015—<ref href="/us/pl/114/54">Pub. L. 114–54</ref> substituted “<date date="2020-09-30">September 30, 2020</date>” for “<date date="2015-09-30">September 30, 2015</date>”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2010—<ref href="/us/pl/111/239">Pub. L. 111–239</ref> substituted “<date date="2015-09-30">September 30, 2015</date>” for “<date date="2010-09-30">September 30, 2010</date>”.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="ideedf6fee-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="ideedf6fef-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Mandatory Livestock Reporting Extension</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/118/83/dA">Pub. L. 118–83, div. A</ref>, §§ 106(3), 120, <date date="2024-09-26">Sept. 26, 2024</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/138/1526">138 Stat. 1526</ref>, 1528, as amended by <ref href="/us/pl/118/158/dA/s101/1">Pub. L. 118–158, div. A, § 101(1)</ref>, <date date="2024-12-21">Dec. 21, 2024</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/138/1723">138 Stat. 1723</ref>, extended the termination date for authority provided by this subchapter from <date date="2024-09-30">September 30, 2024</date>, to <date date="2025-03-14">Mar. 14, 2025</date>.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/116/260/dO/tIV/s401">Pub. L. 116–260, div. O, title IV, § 401</ref>, <date date="2020-12-27">Dec. 27, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/2149">134 Stat. 2149</ref>, extended the termination date for authority provided by this subchapter from <date date="2020-09-30">September 30, 2020</date>, to <date date="2021-09-30">September 30, 2021</date>.</p>
</note>
